[0.000, "o", "\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[2mInteract with ServiceNow instances via the jsn CLI. Use when working with ServiceNow\r\n\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m  development, administration, or data exploration. Handles tables, records, business rules,\r\n\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m  flows, script includes, ACLs, update sets, and more. Triggered by ServiceNow URLs\r\n\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m  (service-now.com, servicenow.com) or when the user mentions ServiceNow, jsn, servicenow,\r\n\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m  or related terms like tables, records, business rules, flows, script includes, ACLs,\r\n\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m  update sets, or encoded queries.\r\n\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[22m\r\n"]
