[0.001, "o", "\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[0.004, "o", "A CLI for exploring and managing ServiceNow instances.\r\n\r\nOutput modes (pick one):\r\n  --json     JSON envelope {ok, data, summary, breadcrumbs} — use when parsing\r\n  --md       Markdown tables — use when showing results to humans\r\n  --quiet    Raw JSON data only (no envelope)\r\n  --agent    JSON + quiet + no interactive prompts (for automation)\r\n  --jq <f>   Apply jq filter to JSON output\r\n\r\nDiscovery:\r\n  jsn commands --md       Full command catalog with descriptions and hints\r\n  jsn <command> --help    Detailed usage for any command\r\n\r\nHierarchy: Use specific commands (rules, flows, etc.) first. Fall back to\r\n'records --table <name>' for generic CRUD. Use 'rest' as a raw escape hatch.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "Usage:\r\n  jsn [command]\r\n\r\nAvailable Commands:\r\n  acls             Manage Access Control Lists (ACLs)\r\n  assignment-rules Manage assignment rules (sysrule_assignment)\r\n  auth             Manage ServiceNow authentication\r\n  catalog-item     Manage Service Catalog items\r\n  choices          Manage choice values\r\n  client-scripts   Manage client scripts\r\n  code-search      Search code across ServiceNow script tables\r\n  commands         List all available commands\r\n  completion       Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell\r\n  config           Configuration management\r\n  data-policies    Manage data policies\r\n  decision-tables  Manage decision tables (sys_decision)\r\n  docs             Access ServiceNow documentation from sn.jace.pro\r\n  email-actions    Manage email notifications and inbound actions\r\n  eval             Run a background script on the instance\r\n  flows            Manage Flow Designer flows\r\n  forms            Manage UI Forms\r\n  help             Help about any command\r\n  import-sets      Manage import sets and transform maps\r\n  instance         Instance information and diagnostics\r\n  jobs             Manage scheduled jobs/scripts\r\n  lists            Manage UI List layouts\r\n  logs             Query system logs\r\n  records          Manage table records\r\n  rest             Make arbitrary REST API calls\r\n  rules            Manage business rules\r\n  scope            Manage application scopes\r\n  script-includes  Manage script includes\r\n  scripted-rest    Manage Scripted REST APIs\r\n  setup            Interactive first-time setup\r\n  sp               Manage Service Portals\r\n  sp-pages         Manage Service Portal Pages\r\n  sp-widgets       Manage Service Portal Widgets\r\n  tables           Manage tables\r\n  ui-policies      Manage UI policies\r\n  ui-scripts       Manage UI Scripts\r\n  updateset        Manage update sets\r\n  variable         Manage catalog item variables\r\n  variable-types   List catalog variable types\r\n  version          Show version information\r\n\r\nFlags:\r\n      --agent                  Agent mode (JSON + quiet + no interactive prompts)\r\n      --config string          config file (default is $HOME/.config/servicenow/config.json)\r\n  -h, --help                   help for jsn\r\n      --jq string              Apply jq filter to JSON output\r\n      --json                   Output as JSON\r\n      --md                     Output as Markdown\r\n      --no-interactive         Disable interactive prompts (for scripts/CI)\r\n      --no-updateset-warning   Suppress the default update set warning\r\n  -p, --profile string         profile to use\r\n  -q, --quiet                  Quiet output (data only, no envelope)\r\n\r\nUse \"jsn [command] --help\" for more information about a command.\r\n"]
