[0.005, "o", "\r\n╔═══════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n║     Welcome to ServiceNow CLI         ║\r\n╚═══════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\nLet's get you set up. This will only take a moment.\r\n\r\nStep 1: Instance URL\r\n\r\nEnter your ServiceNow instance URL.\r\nExamples:\r\n  https://mycompany.service-now.com\r\n  https://dev12345.service-now.com\r\n\r\nInstance URL: "]
[5.036, "o", "https://dev373698.service-now.com/"]
[0.695, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  ✓ Using: https://dev373698.service-now.com\r\n\r\nStep 2: Profile Name\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "Choose a name for this configuration profile.\r\nExamples: prod, dev, sandbox, mycompany\r\n\r\nProfile name [default]: "]
[2.132, "o", "p"]
[0.103, "o", "d"]
[0.096, "o", "i"]
[1.115, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  ✓ Profile: pdi\r\n\r\nStep 3: Save Location\r\n\r\nWhere should this configuration be saved?\r\n  1) Local (.servicenow/config.json) - project-specific [default]\r\n  2) Global (~/.config/servicenow/config.json) - system-wide\r\n\r\nLocation [1]: "]
[3.429, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nChoose authentication method:\r\n  1) Basic Auth (username/password)\r\n  2) OAuth 2.0 (browser-based, most secure) [default]\r\n  3) g_ck Token (glide cookie)\r\n\r\nMethod [2]: "]
[10.444, "o", "2"]
[0.446, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nOAuth 2.0 Authentication\r\n\r\n"]
